Baatein teri, karte huye

Thak’ke sou jaati hoon, sirhaane aasmaan

Jaane kahan, mudd jaati hain

Dekhte dekhte tujhe ye galliyaan

Teri tarah, hmm khushbu chale

Taare hamari tarah raaton se mile


(Interlude)



Suni nahin,

Zamaane ne teri meri kahaniyaan

Kar de koi,

Nawazishein karam meherbaaniyaan


Ye aarzoo deke dekhe ye duniya

Hum jaise koi deewana hi nahin


Kar de koi,

Nawazishein karam meherbaaniyaan


(Interlude)



Raat andheri mein chup rahe the

Ghum ek savera dhund rahe the

Sadiyon se jaise, jaag rahe the

Pyaar ko apne thaap rahe the


Phir gir pade,

Koi mila na sahara, kya karein


Suni nahin,

Zamaane ne teri meri kahaniyaan



(Interlude)



Tera woh pyaar, yaad aayega

Bhulega na, ye dil mera

Kya ho gaya, socha na tha



Tera woh pyaar, tera woh pyar

Tera woh pyaar, tera woh pyar

Tera woh pyaar, tera woh pyar

Tera woh pyaar, tera woh pyar



Teri woh khamoshiyaan,

kehti thi woh sabhi

Jo tu na, keh saki

Kaise batati tujhe, sharmaati thi main

Jaise aanchal mein jalta diya


Khoye kahan? mujhko bata..


Tere woh pyar, yaad aayega

Bhulega na, ye dil mera


Tera woh pyaar,yaad aayega

Bhulega na, ye dil mera

Kya ho gaya, socha na tha



hoooooo......
